name: VIDEO: County Connection March 2020
description: On this episode, the County's Public Health Laboratory is now able to test for coronavirus (COVID-19), landlords could benefit from a Section 8 housing program, find out why knowing your blood pressure numbers are so important and take a virtual hike at William Heise County Park.

affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office
